Since 2009, in an attempt to "win hearts and minds" and to carry out the impossible task of making aid and offensive actions coincide, a service of "civil-military actions" of the Ministry of Defense (Cimic), suppressed in 2012, carried out, and carried out by a small French NGO, many works of collective interest and agricultural rehabilitation actions in dozens of villages.
